28 SECTION 27. ORS 682.204 is amended to read:
29 682.204. (1) A person may not act as an emergency medical services provider unless the person
30 is licensed under this chapter.
31 (2) A person or governmental unit [which] that operates an ambulance may not authorize [a]
32 another person to act for [it] the person or governmental unit as an emergency medical services
33 provider unless the emergency medical services provider is licensed under this chapter.
